extendedInfo.description: "The Northeast State Community College App provides school information, up to date news and video direct to your Android phone in real-time and for free. Find out what is happening via direct news feeds, Facebook, Twitter and YouTube.Keeping in touch with what is happening at school has never been easier!Northeast State Community College is a comprehensive two-year community college under the governance of the Tennessee Board of Regents of the State University and Community College System of Tennessee. As a comprehensive community college, Northeast State provides university parallel programs designed for students desiring to transfer to another college or university, career programs for students planning to enter the workforce immediately upon graduation, and continuing education and community service programs for professional growth and personal enrichment to the citizens of Carter, Johnson, Sullivan, Unicoi, and Washington Counties.Contact Us at:Northeast State Community College2425 Highway 75 P.O. Box 246 Blountville, Tennessee 37617-0246 Phone: 423.323.3191 or 800.836.7822"
